review.reviewBody: Amazing taste and great variety and best Cali roll so far as not too fishy and tastes fresh. Would love to see Gyu nigiri and beef tataki also. Love Sunflower Sunflower Roll (8 Pcs) as it is hard to find this type of roll. Same roll with juicy mango sauce and mango added is also good so if taking any menu ideas I know those are big favs! Must try.
do not recommend.  the sunomono tasted like water. noodles undercooked.
